title: Adventure Time complete seasons 1 to 5 - 1080p HD
description:
Adventure Time complete seasons 1 to 5 - 1080p HD

This release is based on 1080p downloads from iTunes. The files have not been transcoded at all, to maintain the highest quality possible except for a full bluray rip. For seasons 4 and 5, no higher quality than this is currently available anywhere. The episodes have been split from their double-feature format into individual files, with each one still including the appropriate intro and credits segments. (however, since the credits are written for double-feature broadcasts, they will sometimes mention characters that didn't appear in the individual episodes)

Additionally, custom thumbnails have been made for each episode based on the official promo art.

Example: http://i.imgur.com/G8NPXOs.png

All files are encoded identically. Here is a representative example:
